<br>
Defeat and failure in the War on Terror will bring radical change. It is a pattern repeated throughout history. All kinds of activists and power-seekers know this and hope to pick up the pieces. <br>
It is not the Left that would come to power in America after such a debacle however, though that is avowedly their aim and the likely reason that they increasingly side with people who would otherwise be their mortal enemies (and who were as recently as the Soviet-Afghan war of the 1980s.)<br>
